tags.description: Tregantle Beach is famous for a Lego cargo spill in 1997.  This event spilled millions of pieces of Legos which are still washing up on the beach today.    https://www.inverse.com/article/33669-great-lego-spill-england-pieces-washing-up-on-beach-in-2017
